projects.title: Admin Dashboard.
projects.description: An admin dashboard is a web-based user interface that provides administrators with an overview of critical metrics, data, and functionality. It often includes items such as charts, tables, forms, and navigation. The dashboard enables administrators to efficiently monitor and manage the program or system.
